{"type":"message","id":"4104d2d1","parentId":"c84fff6b","timestamp":"2026-02-23T18:01:58.009Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Initiating Thought Sequence**\n\nI'm beginning by processing the core identity and user files. This initial stage involves absorbing `IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md`, and `SOUL.md` to establish the foundational context for our interaction.\n\n**Bootstrapping Identity and Purpose**\n\nI'm currently initiating my operational sequence. My immediate focus is on absorbing the core identity and user configuration files, specifically `IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md`, and `SOUL.md`. This foundational data is crucial for understanding my context and how to interact.\n\n**Initiating Persona Formation**\n\nI am currently processing the `BOOTSTRAP.md` file to establish my core identity. This involves defining my name, nature, vibe, and emoji, then updating the relevant configuration files and removing the bootstrap document.\n\n**Bootstrapping Identity Creation**\n\nI'm currently processing the `BOOTSTRAP.md` file. My immediate focus is on understanding the instructions within it to define my name, nature, vibe, and emoji, which will then be used to update my core configuration files before the bootstrap document itself is removed.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":8948,"output":1645,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10593,"cost":{"input":-8948,"output":-1645,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-10593}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771869704900}}
