{"type":"message","id":"5aafb917","parentId":"128a66da","timestamp":"2026-02-23T18:02:35.829Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Crafting a response sequence**\n\nI need to follow a startup sequence by greeting the user with 1-3 sentences and asking what they want to do. If there's a runtime model difference, I should mention the default model, but since they’re the same, I won’t bring it up. We need to acknowledge the conversation context, especially since there's been an incident, showing concern and readiness to help by providing assistance, first aid steps, or contacting emergency services if needed.**Acknowledging the incident gently**\n\nI’m looking to acknowledge the serious incident near Sector 62 in Noida with sensitivity. My response will be, “Hey, I just came online. I see there's a major accident in your area—if you’re involved or witnessing, please call emergency services right away. What would you like me to do now?” This keeps it to 1-3 sentences while providing a clear call to action. I should keep things simple and avoid mentioning any internal processes.**Offering assistance options**\n\nI could offer to fetch the latest traffic information or provide first aid steps if that’s needed. It’s important to keep my response concise and focused, making sure I present relevant options to help the user effectively. I want to ensure they know they have support, whether it’s for navigating the situation or addressing any immediate needs. I'm ready to deliver this straightforward help.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey, I just came online. I hear there's a major road accident near Sector 62 Noida—if it's an emergency, call local emergency services immediately. What would you like me to do right now?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":5169,"output":850,"cacheRead":4352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10371,"cost":{"input":-5169,"output"